    "A common method is to include attention checks that only ask the participants to select a specific answer, such as \"Select answer number three\".",
    "All participants who failed to respond to this question correctly could be excluded from further data analysis.",
    "Using crowdsourcing platforms for the recruitment of participants for experiments is big business.",
